         <body view="all">
            <ce:sections>
               <ce:para id="p0005" view="all">This article has been retracted: please see Elsevier Policy on Article Withdrawal (<ce:inter-ref id="interrefs10" xlink:href="https://www.elsevier.com/about/policies/article-withdrawal" xlink:type="simple">https://www.elsevier.com/about/policies/article-withdrawal</ce:inter-ref>).</ce:para>
               <ce:para id="p0006" view="all">This article has been retracted at the request of the Editor-in-Chief.</ce:para>
               <ce:para id="p0007" view="all">Concerns were raised about the similarities between various panels from Figures 2 and 3 and panels from an earlier paper published by the authors in the Journal of Pharmaceutical and Biomedical Analysis 180 (2020) 113050 <ce:inter-ref id="interrefs20" xlink:href="https://nam11.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1016%2Fj.jpba.2019.113050&amp;data=05%7C01%7CM.Grecea%40elsevier.com%7C3478a00d73294d6b1a6d08db3062d9ba%7C9274ee3f94254109a27f9fb15c10675d%7C0%7C0%7C638156973355964028%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=XsPjQd75rlItxpI%2FfHJ6sGup7bNZULCUTMpY6AGuK9A%3D&amp;reserved=0" xlink:type="simple">https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jpba.2019.113050</ce:inter-ref>
               </ce:para>
               <ce:para id="p0008" view="all">The journal requested the authors to provide an explanation regarding these similarities. The authors did not provide a satisfactory explanation in response to these concerns. The Editor-in-Chief assessed this case and decided to retract the article.</ce:para>
            </ce:sections>
         </body>
